1.5.4 - February 23, 2011
- Added Analytics to all products and samples. Gathering basic device data and tracking app state
to determine push conversion related data. Can be enabled/disabled via takeOffOptions, on by default.
- Added cleaner exits and error handling for missing UI classes.

1.5.3 - January 31, 2011
- Updated copyrights
- Updated all projects to use Clang/LLVM 1.6 as default (fully compatible now)

1.5.2 - January 27, 2011
- Fixed dateFormatter to require GMT and en_us_posix locale

1.5.1 - January 20, 2011
- Removed unused class UAInboxDelegate
- Added missing -all_load linker flags

1.5.0 - December 27, 2010
- First Static Library Release

1.4.2 - August 18, 2010

- Fixes issue where default inboxes were not created if a device token was not available.
- Fixes issue where multiple popups would display if an inbox can't be loaded.

1.4.1 - June 28, 2010

- Minor bugfix for iPad layout

1.4.0 - June 24, 2010 (Official Launch)

- Support for callbacks to native code from AirMail message via
  AirMailDefaultJSDelegate
- Improved Caching
- iOS4 compatibility
- Cleaned up internationalization code.
- Tons of bug fixes.

1.3.0 - May 6, 2010

 - iPad support
 - Edit button is now context sensitive, so it will be disabled if
   there are no messages selected.
 - Display "No Messages" to let the user know the inbox is empty
   instead of just showing a blank screen.

1.2.0 - April 16, 2010

  - Offline caching
  - Landscape mode
  - Unread indicator at the top
  - Bulk edit functions (mark as read and delete)
  - Internationalization
  - [Bug] Fixed a memory leak

1.0.0 - March 22, 2010

  - Initial release
